name: Philip from space funeral over week 6 BF.
name_original: Philip from space funeral over week 6 BF.
description:
For some time I've been wishing there was a Space Funeral mod for FNF'.  this isn't really what I had in mind when I said that, but I put like 3 half's a day of work into this  so why not post it.

Here is the art if you want it for some reason. And no the hey dodging doesn't work in game.
